    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Edged weapons consisting basically of a blade, generally longer than that of daggers or knives, and a grip; designed for delivering cutting or thrusting blows or both.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
